<h2 id="c-json-serialize-deserialize"><center>[C#] Json Serialize, Deserialize</center></h2>

<blockquote>
  <p><a href="https://github.com/chanos-dev/blogcode/tree/master/20-1027">Git Source</a></p>
</blockquote>

<hr />

<ul>
  <li>C#에서 Json을 간단하게 컨트롤할 수 있다.</li>
  <li>JsonConvertor 클래스에 Serialize와 Deserialize를 사용하여 간단하게 Json을 직렬화, 역직렬화를 할 수 있고, Nuget에서 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Newtonsoft.Json</code>을 추가하여 사용할 수 있다.</li>
</ul>

<p><a href="http://localhost:4000/images/posts/2020-10-27/Json.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/images/posts/2020-10-27/Json.png" alt="Json" /></a></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Person Class</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>class Person
    {
        public Person() { }

        public string Name;
        public int Age;
        public string Sex;
        public string Address;
        
        public void PrintInfo(object obj, Person person)
        {
            if(obj is TextBox textBox)
            {
                textBox.Text = person.ToString();
            }
        }

        public override string ToString()
        {
            StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
            sb.AppendLine($"Name : {this.Name}");
            sb.AppendLine($"Age : {this.Age}");
            sb.AppendLine($"Sex : {this.Sex}");
            sb.AppendLine($"Address : {this.Address}");

            return sb.ToString();
        }
    }
</code></pre></div></div>

<blockquote>
  <p>Person Class 직렬화</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>private void button_serialize_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)
{
    Person person = new Person();
    person.Name = "홍길동";
    person.Age = 23;
    person.Sex = "남자";
    person.Address = "경기도 광주시";

    string json = JsonConvert.SerializeObject(person);
    textBox1.Text = json;
}
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="--processstart--">- Process.Start -</h3>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>using System.Diagnostics; //추가
...
//응용프로그램 실행
Process.Start("http://www.google.co.kr"); //인터넷 실행

Process.Start("C:\Windows\System32"); //폴더 실행

Process.Start("cmd.exe"); //cmd 실행

//arguments 전달
Process.Start("cmd.exe", "\c ping 8.8.8.8); //cmd - ping 8.8.8.8 커맨드 실행
</code></pre></div></div>
